                    <span>This book is a fine reference to computer scientists who wish to understand the protection and restoration background of different networking techniques such as SONET-SDH, IP and MPLS. This book is also a unique exemplar in the field of network recovery which strengthens its position further. It is well written and easy understandable. 
<br />
<br />I found a very good introduction in each chapter in the book. Each theoretical section is followed by examples that makes the subject more understandable. 
<br />
<br />I highly recommend this book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Excellent, pioneer book!!!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
